                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14388751" author="stack" created="Tue, 31 Mar 2015 16:03:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds good &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=liushaohui&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;liushaohui&quot;&gt;Liu Shaohui&lt;/a&gt; Do you mean adding a label on the Mutation itself? Or do you mean adding a tag?  What label have? &apos;true&apos; if edit was via replication or would it list src cluster ids?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14388875" author="esteban" created="Tue, 31 Mar 2015 17:22:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=liushaohui&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;liushaohui&quot;&gt;Liu Shaohui&lt;/a&gt; how the transitions from this new state will happen? when the delta between the source and the sink is 0? or do we need an operator to perform the transition? wouldn&apos;t be easier just re-use the READONLY attribute from HTD?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14390520" author="liushaohui" created="Wed, 1 Apr 2015 13:18:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=esteban&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;esteban&quot;&gt;Esteban Gutierrez&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;how the transitions from this new state will happen? when the delta between the source and the sink is 0?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes. We need a external tool to check all edits have been replicated to the sink cluster.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or do we need an operator to perform the transition? &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes, we may introduce an new attribute in HTD.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;wouldn&apos;t be easier just re-use the READONLY attribute from HTD?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This new state is used for tables in backup cluster. But the read only table will reject the write operations from replication.&lt;br/&gt;
So we may need to introduce a new attribute.&lt;/p&gt;

</comment>
                            <comment id="14390536" author="liushaohui" created="Wed, 1 Apr 2015 13:25:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=stack&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;stack&quot;&gt;stack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you mean adding a label on the Mutation itself? Or do you mean adding a tag? What label have? &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was thinking just add an attribute in the Mutation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&apos;true&apos; if edit was via replication or would it list src cluster ids?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes, we can just use the number of cluster ids to check if the mutations are from replication.  &lt;br/&gt;
Thanks, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=stack&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;stack&quot;&gt;stack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14391180" author="esteban" created="Wed, 1 Apr 2015 18:38:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=liushaohui&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;liushaohui&quot;&gt;Liu Shaohui&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yes. We need a external tool to check all edits have been replicated to the sink cluster.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think it needs to be done via an external tool since it is hard to guarantee a 0 delta for busy clusters and perhaps every time you run the tool or depending how long it takes to this tool the table state might have changed. I think you can use this label to ship the delta between the edit begin shipped and the latest edit in the source cluster so the sink can track how far is behind and then via a configuration threshold (time based or transaction based) transition the replicated table from this dirty state into consistent state.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14543135" author="liushaohui" created="Thu, 14 May 2015 03:33:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=stack&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;stack&quot;&gt;stack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=esteban&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;esteban&quot;&gt;Esteban Gutierrez&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
The mutations from replication has more than cluster ids in their attribution. So no need to add a replication label.&lt;br/&gt;
I will close this issue if no objections.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
